reviewText: This is included in the DVD collection of I Love Lucy, the complete comedy series. Along with many famous guest stars, it continues the story of Lucy,Ricky, little Ricky, and the Mertzes after they move to the country. The I Love Lucy Collection is worth the price by itself, this is a surprise bonus. If you buy the series at the right time, you can get a great deal on both. This is some of the best material ever on TV.
